{"tid":464480,"cid":1,"subCid":0,"title":"香港做'窮人'真好","createTime":"2017-11-10T14:34:14.000Z","updateTime":"2017-11-10T14:47:54.000Z","uid":143307,"like":1,"dislike":4,"uniUserReply":5,"replies":[{"pid":"4dfe6057e6c3cf1b033e65dc35602d5611b8a0fa","tid":464480,"uid":143307,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2017-11-10T14:34:14.000Z","msg":"有公屋住<br />\n有錢拎<br />\n讀中學唔使錢<br />\n書又唔使錢買<br />\n食飯坐車都有津貼<br />\n考公開試又免費<br />\n讀大學又唔使錢<br />\n<br />\n然後日日可以蒲<br />\n想買乜買乜<br />\n實際有錢過好多人<br />\n<br />\n小弟屋企冇樓<br />\n屋企冇錢<br />\n<br />\n但又冇資助<br />\n冇公屋<br />\n屋企人又辛苦交租<br />\n讀書一年四萬幾真係唔係少<br />\n<br />\n見到假窮人又拎嗮好處<br />\n又有政府養<br />\n過得仲自由自在過好多人<br />\n<br />\n世界真係好唔公平<br />\n<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/frown.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"88365d5aef0c570158ba762e925dcc613f53854c","tid":464480,"uid":64318,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2017-11-10T14:35:34.000Z","msg":"<img src=\"/assets/faces/big/wonder.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> <img src=\"/assets/faces/big/wonder.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> <img src=\"/assets/faces/big/wonder.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> <img src=\"/assets/faces/big/wonder.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"8de7c649da21ce33e3dc4e352dd96344dca54f43","tid":464480,"uid":87506,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2017-11-10T14:37:10.000Z","msg":"係架 咁你想點？"},{"pid":"a2338c7f214f6f0f34a8ce5543e7317d62327032","tid":464480,"uid":11798,"like":0,"dislike":1,"score":-1,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2017-11-10T14:37:55.000Z","msg":"公屋撚中學讀國際學校唔洗錢？"},{"pid":"e2a0fd292331318769bca78a552939f503e28cd1","tid":464480,"uid":82421,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2017-11-10T14:47:54.000Z","msg":"可能淨係你又&quot;窮&quot;又無福利呢<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/chicken.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"}]}